{"tid":1979104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與其懲罰唔夠黃既，不如諗點樣獎勵夠黃既?","createTime":"2020-04-19T07:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T12:40:15.000Z","uid":93141,"like":62,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0f45e982dd467b6d917edfa484e1c23fdd9c973c","tid":1979104,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"講鬥黃呢件事之前，不如大家諗返點樣我地係點樣為裝修訂立標準?<br />\n&ldquo;黑裝修，紅裝飾，藍罷買，黃幫襯&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，我地見到作為對立方既黑紅藍都有根據嚴重性而有唔同行動<br />\n點解要咁做? 就係我地完全唔能原諒既只有黑店，紅藍店都係網開一面，不論真情定假意，都變相鼓勵佢地之後會投入黃色經濟圈作為暫時盟友共同抗敵<br />\n<br />\n作為己方既黃，我地卻都只係一視同仁地單單&ldquo;幫襯&rdquo;而無程度之分<br />\n你默書僅僅合格同你攞滿分，都冇理由拎同樣既禮物<br />\n事實係，黃有等級之分，亦必須有等級之分<br />\n<br />\n想建立黃色經濟圈，只幫襯黃店係必然既事<br />\n但今日如果你同女朋友慶祝生日，同樣既1000蚊，同樣既質素，你會想用落仆心仆命又派物質又罷工既金黃店，定係講一句香港加油既淺黃店?<br />\n<br />\n點解要咁做? 就係我地想更多淺黃店好單純地為利益推動自己成為金黃店。既然加入左黃色經濟圈就係自己人，但亦要論功行賞，先有真正既可持續性同進步空間<br />\n<br />\n點樣做? 就係香港人最鍾意既拉curve<br />\n點拉curve，每人唔同標準，但每人心入面應該要開始有一把尺<br />\n例如下圖係一個假設<br />\n淺黃，我每個月幫襯一兩次。金黃，我每個月幫襯四五次<br />\n淺黃，我個budget最多每人200。金黃，我個budget可以到每人500<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6M4JsR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6M4JsR.png&h=7dfbb11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其我地用屌票形式懲罰唔夠黃既店，不如用獎勵形式鼓勵夠黃既店左榜樣，等唔夠黃既店自己鬥自己，催促自己跟上<br />\n既然叫得自己黃色經濟圈，就應該要用正面公平競爭既方法執行我地獨有既市場機制，令真正黃既店能一直生存，一時偽黃既店就會被我地獨有既市場機制淘汰"},{"pid":"5a5b77570fa026f845cd1fa0191551e01e75d020","tid":1979104,"uid":93141,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"樓主心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c450036c98a686fe4493ece3f7f75a3927573fd","tid":1979104,"uid":93141,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a5b77570fa026f845cd1fa0191551e01e75d020","tid":1979104,"uid":93141,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"樓主心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"樓主精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3ae828285e3399f5476dab65618ac6270a1e80","tid":1979104,"uid":93141,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4c450036c98a686fe4493ece3f7f75a3927573fd","tid":1979104,"uid":93141,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a5b77570fa026f845cd1fa0191551e01e75d020","tid":1979104,"uid":93141,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"樓主心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"樓主精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:44:53.000Z","msg":"唔記得轉account咋on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc720dfa303d392015fdf9ef1437d2278b725542","tid":1979104,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 竟然有圖"},{"pid":"72810444944adaf98168d8404d25a43df0e4d9b9","tid":1979104,"uid":133903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"c0b17ea76fa9b6f62068f09b6d74a5f323b04eb3","tid":1979104,"uid":93141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bc720dfa303d392015fdf9ef1437d2278b725542","tid":1979104,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 竟然有圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"職業病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492705c39b0539144a2bc20b2ef1e4d15dbd65d